						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Broken slab built into the plinth of Kallēśvara temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>13th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This fragmentary record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">13th Century A.D.,</hi> registers a gift of land by several individuals of whom the names of Bhīma-Bhaṭṭa and Nīlakaṇṭha-Bhaṭṭa are preserved. It records further gifts by the sons of Ayaṁgaḷu. The details are lost.</p>						

						</summary>
